      {
        "paragraph_index": 3,
        "text": "### Recommended Follow-Up\n\nTo obtain the **exact overlap count** and a systematic Δlog β table, the following query would work:\n\n```sql\nSELECT c.ligand_id, c.ligand_name_SRD\nFROM ligandmetal_card c\nWHERE c.metal_id IN (61, 62)\nGROUP BY c.ligand_id\nHAVING COUNT(DISTINCT c.metal_id) = 2\n```\n\nThis would yield the precise number of shared ligands and enable a matched-condition comparison of log β values for each.\n\n*All counts sourced from NIST SRD-46 (metal_61 = Fe³⁺, metal_62 = Fe²⁺).*",
